Here’s a scenario:
<br />

<br />
I’m in ME fighting 4 Arms and get three on the pull… I slow all and start trying to take them out one by one. Now, I have them all hitting me so keeping Fluffy on one particular mob isn’t a problem until pet push places the mob far enough out for the other two to hit my pet. At this point my stupid pet always wants to change targets to what’s hitting it rather than what I want it to attack(Maybe your pets a bit smarter but mines stupid like that… no treat for joo Fluffy!) 
<br />

<br />
Will this ability allow me to have my pet stay on one mob no matter what? 
<br />

